<p>See <a href="../../../index.html?page_id=3">Hugo Award Categories</a> for a more detailed discussion of the categories. The technical definitions of the categories are in the current version of the <a href="http://midamericon2.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/WSFS-Constitution-as-of-September-2015.pdf">WSFS Constitution</a>, and those technical definitions take priority in case of any ambiguity. Decisions regarding eligibility are made by the current year&#8217;s Hugo Administration Subcommittee, whose decisions are final in all cases.</p>





